Federation Commons Addendum:

This project incorporates federation patterns and architectural concepts 
inspired by Bonfire Networks and the broader ActivityPub ecosystem. While 
this project is MIT licensed, integration with AGPL-licensed components 
from the Bonfire ecosystem is achieved through clean-room implementation 
and selective pattern adoption, maintaining license compatibility.

Thunderline Distributed Intelligent Operating System, PAC agents, and 
Thunderblock federation concepts are original intellectual property of 
the Thunderblok Federation Development Team.

